ACFC Players Player of the Year: 2005/06
ACFC Supporters: Player of the Year 2007/08
ACFC Golden Boot: 2005/06 &amp; 2008/09
ACFC Personality of the Year: 2007/08
Chatham Cup Winners: 2007
FIFA Club World Cup: 2006, 2009
Oceania Champions League Winners: 2006 &amp; 2009

